Enum Class RepastNervousSystemElementFactory

public enum RepastNervousSystemElementFactory extends Enum<RepastNervousSystemElementFactory> implements NervousSystemElementFactory
Factory class for creating instances of various nervous system elements in the Repast Simphony framework. This class implements the singleton pattern using an enum.
